# textutils
Developed a dynamic web application using the Django framework to provide a text utility service. The website offers a range of text manipulation and analysis features, enhancing user productivity and efficiency. Implemented various functionalities, including text formatting, character/word count, text case conversion, URL encoding/decoding, and text summarization. Utilized Django's model-view-template (MVT) architecture, ensuring efficient data handling and seamless user interaction. Incorporated responsive design principles, ensuring optimal user experience across different devices. Employed HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to create an intuitive and visually appealing user interface. Integrated with a back-end MySQL database for data storage and retrieval. Implemented user authentication and authorization using Django's built-in authentication system. Collaborated with a team of developers and followed agile methodologies to meet project timelines. Employed version control using Git for efficient code management.
